  "paragraphs": [
    "Product only. Pricing exclusions apply. Contact a dealer for more information.",
    "Evoke an open-hearth experience so real, friends may ask to add another log to the fire. We pioneered the open gas fireplace with a large, glass-free view so you get the ultimate combination of authenticity and innovation. Mild heat settings allow for openness without feeling overheated, and you can even stream your tunes or the crackling of a fire through built-in Bluetooth speakers. Not available in Canada.",
    "Experience easy, convenient control to fit your lifestyle. See your dealer for details.",
    "Enhance the appearance of your hearth product with decorative items for the customized fireside experience you want.",
    "Add a finishing touch to enhance your fireplace and distinguish your home. Browse fireplace fronts that frame your opening and glass or mesh doors in colors to complement your décor. Colors on screen can vary. Connect with your local dealer online or in person to see actual samples.",
